# File: app/styles/ie.css.ab
# Purpose: Empty Compass IE-specific override stylesheet placeholder stored in app/styles/
# Dependencies: []

## Overview
An empty CSS file serving as the Compass placeholder for Internet Explorer-specific override styles. Contains only the standard Compass generator comment instructing how to import it via conditional comments (`<!--[if IE]>...`). No IE-specific overrides have been authored. This is the older `app/styles/` location equivalent of `app/assets/css/ie.css`.

## Interface
No exports. Empty placeholder stylesheet.

## Dependencies
No project-level dependencies.

## Implementation Notes
- 1 line — only the Compass IE override comment, no actual CSS rules
- Generated by the Yeoman Angular generator's Compass scaffold
- No IE-specific styles have been defined for the TuyoTools frontend
- Counterpart: `app/assets/css/ie.css` (also empty, with a CSS source map reference)
